name: Catstronaut (Julian Vos)
description:
Catstronaut is a browser game in which you, a Catstronaut, embark on an adventure through space to retrieve your lost kittens.

Works best in Chromium-based browsers.

Made in three days by:

  • Jessica Sies - Art and Narrative
  • Jessie Stam - GUI programming
  • Julian Vos - Gameplay programming
  • Michel Ivulic - Music and SFX
